plist_data.NSCameraDeniedDescription: You have denied Agape's camera access. You can still enjoy all AI coaching and climbing features except camera-based ones.
plist_data.NSCameraUsageDescription: Enable Agape's camera access. Capture climbing moments or scan QR codes for gear and safety. Your privacy is always respected.
plist_data.NSLocalNetworkUsageDescription: Agape may use local network access for device discovery or enhanced climbing experiences. No personal data is shared without your permission.
plist_data.NSMicrophoneDeniedDescription: If you deny Agape's microphone permission, you can still use text chat and all other features. Voice features will be disabled.
plist_data.NSMicrophoneUsageDescription: Allow Agape to use your microphone for voice chat with AI coaches or recording climbing notes. Your voice data is only used for enhancing your experience.
plist_data.NSPhotoLibraryDeniedDescription: You have denied Agape's access to your photo library. You can still use all core features, but cannot upload or share photos from your device.
plist_data.NSPhotoLibraryUsageDescription: Grant Agape access to your photo library to upload climbing photos, customize your profile, or share achievements. Your photos are never shared without your consent.
plist_data.NSUserTrackingUsageDescription: Agape values your privacy. We only collect necessary data to improve your climbing and AI coaching experience. Your information is always secure.
